<p><a name="Life-Cycle" id="Life-Cycle"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=OSGi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Life-Cycle">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Life-Cycle</span></h2>
<table class="metadata plainlinks ambox mbox-small-left ambox-notice" style="margin: 4px 1em 4px 0; width: 238px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 88%; line-height: 1.25em;">
