<td class="mbox-text" style="">This section requires <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=OSGi&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=OSGi&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">expansion</a>.</td>
